      <p>Vue MDL is a set of reusable <a target="_blank" href="http://www.getmdl.io/">Material Design Lite</a>(mdl) components. Its purpose is to make it easy for everyone to use mdl by doing all the data binding and giving you the control over classes with props. If you find any bug feel free to open an issue, or even better a Pull Request in the github.</p>

      <p>Vue MDL is only available through <code>npm</code>. Install it:
        <pre><code v-highlight>npm install --save vue-mdl</code></pre>
