      <p>Add <code>.min</code> to get the minified version:</p>

      <pre><code v-highlight class="html">&lt;script src=&quot;//rawgit.com/posva/vue-mdl/master/dist/vue-mdl.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</code></pre>

